Text:
Happey New 2011 with this nice remake from the 2005 movie with the same name with Angelina Jolie and Johny Depp .
A little plot here :
A woman named Elise (Jolie) is being trailed in Paris by a number of men who work for Scotland Yard. At a cafe, she receives a letter from Alexander Pearce, a former lover, with explicit directions to board a train to Venice, Italy, pick out a man who resembles him and make the police believe that this man is Alexander Pearce. A mysterious stranger, not involved with the police, also seems to be watching Elise. Elise burns the letter and boards a train.

HAPPY 2011 !!!

The subtitles are in Russian, not English, ergo, unless you speak Italian or read Russian, some of the movie is lost on you. I d/l'd using the magnet link, which only gave me the movie file and not the other 2, so I'll d/l the 1st file in hopes that it's a subtitle file. Oh, A: 8, V: 9. Good upload, partner.
OK, neither of the other files are subs, so hopefully I can learn working Italian with Rosetta Stone before I watch. That or immerse myself in Cryllic Russian.
